Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,寄宿生？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,住在外國人家裡的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪個國家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,英國！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要去媽媽的朋友家叨擾一個星期左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不過忍 你不是不會講英語嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好過分 還是能說一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,像Hello之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,別的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsudon之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:27.18,tips,,0,0,0,,註：豬排飯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是英語借詞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我會每天祈禱忍能平安回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡好像有個和我同年齡的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 能成為朋友就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,會是怎樣的女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎你 小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面 多有打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的金色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子比較怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,直接進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好有外國的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這是客廳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,盥洗室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有要洗的衣服的話就直接說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,7點吃晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還有什麼想問我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 那個女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好像……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,波比 回小屋裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 她想和你做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫大宮忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,大咪咪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我忍就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字叫愛麗絲·卡爾特萊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,金髮！金髮蘿莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲一一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼快就打成一片了呢……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,日本的女生好可怕啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能合你口味就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 味道怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,甜點不吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,OH！有日本妹子要來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可我又不會說日語……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 卡蓮 在她寄宿期間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你就假裝是我妹妹 過來一起住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不對喲 我才是姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 明天開始我就要去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,卡蓮家好喜歡旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,鐺鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,來 這個奇怪的人偶送給你做護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就算語言不同 一定也能心靈相通的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,卡蓮總說得這麼輕鬆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,來 波比 來這裡 來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子 波比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你弄癢我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,波比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子有好好道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 這不是愛麗絲的錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你熱一杯牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,非常暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,謝…謝 Thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你不生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 非常暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,作為謝禮 能稍微過來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這是從日本帶來的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,本來是想昨天就給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是姐姐幫忙選的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她說這個比較適合送給外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這個呢 要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哦～原來是插在頭髮上的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 我知道了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎是要插在頭髮上然後卷起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我卷～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我卷～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒能派上用場 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,當做筷子來用也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 你會做點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要攪拌得均匀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,過來過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,明天送你去機場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,來玩花牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 花牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不知道規則
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,百人一首……笑臉福神？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 第一次看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她問你真的是日本人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,純度100％啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 水溫怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那是櫻花香味的入浴劑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這裡好像不習慣泡澡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要浸到肩膀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這個就是日本的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 我覺得暈暈的……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可以一起睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,日本是個什麼樣的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan…日本？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,日本現在是早上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真神奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡明明還是晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的太陽卻已經升起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有種只有我們被拋在世界一角的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這種話題小綾大概會比較喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 小綾是我在學校的……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好想未來有一天可以去日本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙您的照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要再來玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,回頭把照片寄給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你好一一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,日本……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 起床了 要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,忍～?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 快去上學啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早安…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,然後啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 因為讀了一下信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,信？哇 航空郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是以前去英國寄宿的家庭寄來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 愛麗絲寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哦 好厲害 從夢中仙境寄來的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是英國啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是全都是英語 我看不懂 正煩惱著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是說讀了一下嗎 讓我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 真的都是英語呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear 忍～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是大宮忍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你可是高中生了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個都待會兒再說了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這是第一次收到信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 到底寫了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒辦法啊 給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我想是說要到日本來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害 綾能看懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,信上有沒有寫什麼時候能過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 不要辜負忍的期望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真囉嗦啊 陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的學校 高興 制服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,高興的制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 忍 鞋子！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 那邊的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 金髮少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,請問您認識一位叫做忍的女孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 忍？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 我沒有她現在的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是一個和這個人偶長得一樣的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太失禮了喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 在這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,卡爾特萊同學 走這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦斯響板？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是個挺歡樂的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才的女孩穿著我們的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不 比起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在怎麼看忍都像圓頭木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你更在意這個啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 早安！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大宮同學 今天也很有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,請進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,忍！忍！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見了 真的來日本了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我是為了見忍而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲會說日語了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我認真學習了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害 但是為什麼到這裡來？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,卡爾特萊同學 先從自我介紹開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面 我叫愛麗絲·卡爾特萊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,從英國轉學而來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,才注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,信裡寫了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但全是英語…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在第二頁用羅馬字寫了一遍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,綾！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}竟然剛進高中就有外國人轉入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}頭髮和瞳孔都像人偶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}是呀是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}好想給她換上一身禮裙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}放在玻璃櫃里欣賞一整天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}只是說笑而已 請笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}我還以為是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}來 寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}小路…綾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}豬熊陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}野豬的豬 灰熊的熊 豬熊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}是不是有強大帥氣的感覺呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}我…我 食物 不好吃 饒命…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}棒讀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}那個髮簪真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}啊 這個是忍寄宿的時候給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}啊 那時候的東西你到現在還珍惜著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}但我之前以為髮簪是用來捅人的武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}你要當殺手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}在日本的時候住在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}妳是一個人來的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}啊 嗯 我打算去忍家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}怎麼會…獨身一人 無家可歸地…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}住到我家來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}雖是陋室 但卻有我！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}那個 我本來就打算…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1350,1040)}啊哈哈 這兩個人真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小女叫愛麗絲 還請您關照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽明知道愛麗絲會來還保密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可嚇着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是想嚇嚇你而已啦 對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你的日語說得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.92,0:22:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,正座也好標準呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我學習了很多日本的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還穿過一次和服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.59,0:22:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,正座固然辛苦 但穿和服更是又重又熱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,十二層衣物的重量 大還有十公斤左右
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我堅信只要經受往這種考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就能成為合格的大和撫子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼辛苦的話就不要再堅持啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便坐就可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在我家裡不用客氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:22:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 小小薄禮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 太周到啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在飛機場買的銅鑼燒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,日本貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.23,0:23:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻花綻放的時節
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,來自英國的少女住到我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 歡迎來到日本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的房間是西洋風哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,洗澡是用圖式鐵桶浴盆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是西洋風的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time～
